---
title: Italian Beef Meatball Soup with Potato, Leek & Double Parmesan
description: Nothing suits a cold night more than a bowl of warm, steamy soup. This bowl of pure Italian comfort is packed wiith
a garden’s worth of veggies! The addition of savoury beef meatballs make this dish extra hearty, and a sprinkle of
Parmesan over the top gives just the right amount of rich cheesiness.
